{"title":"(14) implementacion-amb-sysmayal2 - Raven","url":"https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-implementacion-amb-sysmayal2","summary":"This page documents the implementation progress of the Raven AI Agent for AMB-Wellness ERPNext system. The content covers Phase 4 - Advanced Analytics & Reporting Module deployment, including new dashboard commands for manufacturing, quality, and financial metrics. Additionally, the page contains a detailed bug report for the sales order to invoice pipeline (QTN-0754 Calipso s.r.l), identifying 5 critical issues: the !delivery command not executing properly, missing stock handling for migrations, missing mandatory CFDI fields for Mexico invoicing, missing product service key on Item 0308, and Serial and Batch Bundle handling requirements for ERPNext v16. The development team is working on fixes for these bugs to complete the sales pipeline from Quote to Sales Invoice.","key_points":["Phase 4 Advanced Analytics & Reporting Module deployed with 4 files pushed to main branch","New dashboard commands available: manufacturing, quality, financial, and overview dashboards","Analytics commands include trend analysis, daily/weekly/monthly reports, and alert configuration","Manufacturing agent supports work order creation, planning, batch management, and production tracking","Bug 1: !delivery command ignores ! prefix - both preview and execute return same response","Bug 2: No stock handling for migration scenarios - needs Stock Reconciliation or --force flag","Bug 3: Sales Invoice missing mandatory CFDI fields: mx_payment_option, mode_of_payment, mx_product_service_key","Bug 4: Item 0308 missing mx_product_service_key field - needed for Mexico CFDI compliance","Bug 5: Serial and Batch Bundle required for ERPNext v16 - old batch_no field deprecated","Current pipeline blocked at Sales Invoice creation due to above bugs","Executive summary shows zero revenue MTD, zero orders, and 0% fulfillment rate","PPD/PUE logic needed for payment terms: 30+ days = PPD, immediate = PUE","CFDI use codes: G01 for goods, G03 for expenses, S01 for services"],"relevant_links":["https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-quality","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-marketing","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-manufacturing","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-batch-lote102"],"file_name":"raven_amb_wellness_phase4_implementation.json"}
